Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:44.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:54.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:59.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:02.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:11.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs140\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,130.389)}The Shocker Graveyard:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,730.389)}Monsters Revived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't catch anything today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should stick to the usual spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's head home for the day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We need humans who\Nsurvive our aptitude test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Kato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take you\Nto the Shocker Graveyard alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and use you as a sacrifice\Nin our devil festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:44.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Shocker's Graveyard in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The crosses mark\Nthe bodies of the cyborgs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who died at the hands\Nof the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here in the Shocker Graveyard,\Nthe devil festival is about to commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Leader of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the limitless power of the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to bestow revival energy\Nupon this cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For each sacrifice of the devil festival,\Nwe can revive five cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Kamen Rider and\Nhis friends to the devil festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That will let us revive\Nall of the buried cyborgs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! Shocker revival energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Harinezuras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaguar Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanjioh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been restored to life\Nwith Shocker's revival energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with Kamikirikid and bring the Kamen\NRider and his allies to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamikirikid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you fight the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you should undergo\Ntraining with the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who have experienced loss\Nat the Kamen Rider's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, try the Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What, is that all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Rider Kick is ten\Ntimes stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're raring to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell! We've found Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Make contact at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck did Hongo get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have at least dropped\Na line to let me know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The wire's been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess someone snuck into the room, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking into someone's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo sent me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've escaped from Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in danger,\Nand Mr. Hongo saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And he told you to come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.\NI'll keep you safe, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're after me, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who learn Shocker's\Nsecrets must not escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back to life to\Ncontinue to spread evil, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rematch between\NKamen Rider and the cyborgs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got it!\N- Get to the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran away from Shocker, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They've brought back cyborgs\Nthat Rider beat in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He has to fight\Nall those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be too much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tachibana Racing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we're surrounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We should come out with our hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to at least get Mr. Kato to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cause any more trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everyone, barricade the door.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Emi, hurry!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Block the window.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, grab weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that man to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... run, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, Shocker's after this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kato, go with Rider, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm going to take\Nthis man somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Taki!\N- Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grab on tight!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight. Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my big chance, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a major miscalculation this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's real target\Nwas you, Taki, and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kamikirikid, and I was\Nborn to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, Tachibana and the others\Nare under attack as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:57.48,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider already took\Nthe man you were after!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were really getting\NKamen Rider out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with us to\Nthe Shocker Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and take part in the devil festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's us you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won't be part of some devil festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all going to be sacrifices\Nto bring our cyborgs back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sacrificed at the devil\Nfestival in the Shocker Graveyard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... you're going to sacrifice\NTaki and the others, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any who oppose Shocker must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish this later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.92,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:58.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,We've taken your allies to serve\Nas sacrifices for the devil festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rider! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to this Shocker Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hell Valley...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Shocker's Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Behind those rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Leader of Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the limitless power of evil\Nand the blood of these sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to restore our cyborgs to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer the evil spirits of\Nthe altar to the sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer. Suffer more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The greater your suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the more powerful the devil\Nfestival becomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer! Keep suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Get everyone to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:21.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:27.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:35.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:09.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:16.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:24.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:28.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:32.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:54.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Swimming through the\Noceans with a Rider Swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:22:01.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great dive flitting through the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:06.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up whirlpools with a Rider Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:09.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dragging enemies down with a Rider Lung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:13.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!\NRider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:17.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, I've finished off the combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You look after Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Where's Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's our guardian angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider brought\Nan end to the Shocker Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what new scheme was\NShocker plotting against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:07.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:10.47,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.72,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:14.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:15.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Girizames.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker commanders arrive from\Ncountries all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:22.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rider and Girizames face off with the\Nfate of their top secret plan on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what is the Shocker\Nleader's true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:27.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Shocker\NLeader Appears!! Rider in Peril."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.71,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,730.389)}The Shocker Leader Appears!! Rider in Peril
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:40.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:44.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:48.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:03.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:07.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:10.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:15.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Graveyard: Monsters Revived
Comment: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker\NLeader Appears!! Rider in Peril